            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-title",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 16,
              "width": 800,
              "height": 52,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#f1f5f9;'>💧 Liquidity Pools & The AMM Formula</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#f1f5f9"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-sub",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 66,
              "width": 800,
              "height": 30,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;color:#64748b;'>No order books. No market makers. Just math — High School Level</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#64748b"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-intro",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 112,
              "width": 950,
              "height": 60,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:15px;color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.7;'>Traditional exchanges match buyers with sellers via order books. DEXs use <b style='color:#f59e0b;'>liquidity pools</b> — smart contracts holding two tokens that anyone can trade against. The price is set automatically by a formula, not by humans.</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#cbd5e1"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-formula-bg",
              "type": "shape",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 186,
              "width": 300,
              "height": 130,
              "rotate": 0,
              "path": "M 0 0 L 1 0 L 1 1 L 0 1 Z",
              "viewBox": [
                1,
                1
              ],
              "fill": "#3b82f615",
              "fixedRatio": false,
              "outline": {
                "style": "solid",
                "width": 2,
                "color": "#3b82f6"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-formula-t",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 34,
              "top": 196,
              "width": 280,
              "height": 110,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:32px;font-weight:900;color:#60a5fa;text-align:center;'>x × y = k</p><p style='font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;margin-top:8px;'>x = token A reserve<br/>y = token B reserve<br/>k = constant product</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#60a5fa"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-how",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 340,
              "top": 186,
              "width": 634,
              "height": 130,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;'>When you <b style='color:#10b981;'>buy</b> token A: its supply in the pool drops → k must stay constant → token A's price rises automatically.<br/>When you <b style='color:#f87171;'>sell</b> token A: its supply increases → price falls automatically.<br/>No human sets the price — it's pure math responding to supply changes.</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-provide-h",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 332,
              "width": 460,
              "height": 26,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#10b981;'>How you provide liquidity (become an LP)</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#10b981"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-provide-b",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 360,
              "width": 460,
              "height": 130,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:2;'>1. Deposit equal value of both tokens (e.g. $500 ETH + $500 USDC)<br/>2. Receive LP tokens = your share of the pool<br/>3. Earn % of every swap fee (usually 0.3%) proportional to your share<br/>4. Withdraw anytime by burning your LP tokens<br/>→ <b style='color:#f59e0b;'>Risk: impermanent loss</b> (next slide)</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-dex-bg",
              "type": "shape",
              "left": 514,
              "top": 332,
              "width": 460,
              "height": 158,
              "rotate": 0,
              "path": "M 0 0 L 1 0 L 1 1 L 0 1 Z",
              "viewBox": [
                1,
                1
              ],
              "fill": "#f59e0b08",
              "fixedRatio": false,
              "outline": {
                "style": "solid",
                "width": 1,
                "color": "#f59e0b30"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-defi-s1-dex-t",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 524,
              "top": 342,
              "width": 440,
              "height": 138,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b;margin-bottom:8px;'>DeFi Building Blocks</p><p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:2;'>🔄 DEX — Trade tokens from your wallet, no sign-up<br/>🏦 Lending — Deposit collateral, borrow against it<br/>🌾 Yield Farming — Provide LP tokens, earn protocol rewards<br/>⚖️ Stablecoins — $1-pegged tokens to hold value in DeFi</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#f59e0b"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "actions": [
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_0",
          "type": "spotlight",
          "elementId": "hs-defi-s1-title"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_1",
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Liquidity Pools and the AMM Formula — High School Level. DeFi is banking without banks. Financial services built on smart contracts — no company runs them.",
          "audioUrl": "/audio/lessons/oc-hs-defi/0-1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_2",
          "type": "spotlight",
          "elementId": "hs-defi-s1-intro"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_3",
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Traditional exchanges match buyers with sellers via order books. DEXs use liquidity pools — smart contracts holding two tokens that anyone can trade against. The price is set automatically by a formula, not by humans.",
          "audioUrl": "/audio/lessons/oc-hs-defi/0-3.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_4",
          "type": "spotlight",
          "elementId": "hs-defi-s1-formula-t"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_5",
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "The formula is x times y equals k. X is the token A reserve. Y is the token B reserve. K is a constant that never changes. When you buy token A, its supply in the pool drops — so k must stay constant, meaning token A's price rises automatically. When you sell, price falls. No human sets the price.",
          "audioUrl": "/audio/lessons/oc-hs-defi/0-5.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_6",
          "type": "spotlight",
          "elementId": "hs-defi-s1-provide-b"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_7",
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "To provide liquidity: deposit equal value of both tokens, for example five hundred dollars in ETH and five hundred in USDC. You receive LP tokens representing your share. You earn a percentage of every swap fee — usually 0.3% — proportional to your share. Withdraw anytime by burning your LP tokens. The risk is impermanent loss, which we'll cover next.",
          "audioUrl": "/audio/lessons/oc-hs-defi/0-7.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_8",
          "type": "spotlight",
          "elementId": "hs-defi-s1-dex-t"
        },
        {
          "id": "action_hs-defi-s1_9",
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "The four DeFi building blocks: DEXs let you trade tokens from your wallet with no sign-up. Lending protocols let you deposit collateral and borrow against it. Yield farming rewards you for providing LP tokens. And stablecoins are dollar-pegged tokens that let you hold value in DeFi without converting back to fiat.",
          "audioUrl": "/audio/lessons/oc-hs-defi/0-9.mp3"
        }
      ]
    },
