              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;color:#60a5fa;'>XRPL has a native DEX and AMM built into the protocol — no smart contracts needed. Trading has been live on-chain since 2012. OnlyCrypto payouts go directly to your wallet in seconds — no custody risk.</p>",
